<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Identity and Address Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            text-align: center;
            width: 300px;
            border: 1px solid #ececec;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .step {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .description {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .info-item {
            text-align: left;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .info-item span {
            color: #7a5af8;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        .info-item .value {
            color: #111;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }
        .info-item .check {
            color: #4caf50;
            margin-left: 5px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #7a5af8;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 14px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #6b46c1;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .footer .brand {
            font-family: 'Pacifico', cursive;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">Logoipsum</div>
        <div class="step">STEP 1 of 2</div>
        <h2 class="title">Your Identity and Address</h2>
        <p class="description">The following information was securely fetched from your DigiLocker account.</p>
        <div class="info-item"><span>👤</span> Full Name <span class="value">Your name</span></div>
        <div class="info-item"><span>📅</span> Date of Birth <span class="value">10/02/1990</span> <span class="check">✔</span></div>
        <div class="info-item"><span>🪪</span> PAN Number <span class="value">XXXXX-XXX-1234</span></div>
        <div class="info-item"><span>🛡️</span> Aadhaar Number <span class="value">XXXXX-XXX-1234</span></div>
        <div class="info-item"><span>🏠</span> Present Address <span class="value">Indu Dreams, Flat 106/108, Rajaram Puri 3rd Lane, Kolhapur, Maharashtra 416001</span></div>
        <button class="button">Next: Your Work Profile</button>
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="brand">truebg</div>
            <small>Copyright © 2025 Truebg. All Rights Reserved.</small>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>